Well, Bryan was never the sharpest crayon in the box, and as for Chris
Huff...er....moon, well, I shall reserve comment because I am in a
good mood and don&#39;t want to spoil it. 

A has-been and a never-was still continuing to cash in on others hard
work and ideas. Sad part is, the cycle just keeps repeating.

Andy



